9:["$","$1","c",{"children":[["$","main",null,{"className":"pb-16 text-brand-ink","children":["$","section",null,{"className":"px-4 py-12 sm:py-16","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"page-shell","children":["$","article",null,{"className":"max-w-3xl mx-auto","children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"text-xs sm:text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-brand-ink/50","children":"Guide / 2026 报税"}],["$","h1",null,{"className":"mt-2 text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-semibold leading-tight","children":"F1/OPT 学生 W-2 缺失补救指南 (2026版)(附 PDF 下载)"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-pink max-w-none mt-10","children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"text-brand-ink/75 leading-7","children":"3 月已经过半，身边的小伙伴都拿到了退税，而你连 W-2 还没影？别担心，这并不意味着你无法报税或身份会受损。针对 2026 报税季，我们整理了这份『救命指南』，帮你通过合法途径补救缺失材料。"}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold mt-12 mb-6 text-brand-ink","children":"第一步：了解 IRS 的正式截止日 (Internal Revenue Service Rules)"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-brand-ink/75 leading-7","children":["首先请保持冷静。根据 IRS 规定，雇主必须在 ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"2026 年 1 月 31 日"}]," 之前寄出（Postmark）W-2 表格。考虑到邮寄时间，如果你在 2 月中旬还没收到，才需要开始采取行动。"]}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold mt-12 mb-6 text-brand-ink","children":"第二步：联系雇主"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-brand-ink/75 leading-7","children":"这是最有效的方式。有些公司可能因为地址更新不及时导致投递失败，或者你可以直接索要 PDF 电子版。"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"my-6 rounded-2xl bg-[#f2dac4]/50 border border-[#e6b8a2]/40 p-5 shadow-sm","children":["$","p",null,{"className":"text-brand-ink/80 leading-7","children":["💡 ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"沟通小贴士："}]," 优先联系 Payroll 部门而非直属老板。你可以询问：'Is my W-2 available for download on ADP/Workday?' 很多时候公司已经上传到了电子平台，只是你没收到纸质信件。"]}]}],["$","$Lc",null,{"subject":"Request for Form W-2 for Tax Year 2025 - [Your Full Name]","template":"Dear [HR Name or Payroll Department],\n\nI am writing to inquire about my Form W-2 for the 2025 tax year. As of today, March 8, 2026, I have not yet received the document at my current mailing address.\n\nCould you please verify if the form has been mailed out? If possible, I would greatly appreciate a digital copy (PDF) for my records to ensure I can file my taxes on time.\n\nMy Details:\n* Full Name: [Your Name]\n* Last 4 Digits of SSN: [XXXX]\n* Employment Period: [e.g., June 2025 - Dec 2025]\n\nThank you for your time and assistance.\n\nBest regards,\n[Your Name]\n[Your Phone Number]"}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold mt-12 mb-6 text-brand-ink","children":"第三步：身份确认"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-brand-ink/75 leading-7","children":["在联系雇主之前，请先确认你今年的报税身份。因为如果你已转为 ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"Resident"}],"，你需要的可能是 W-2；如果你仍是 ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"Non-resident"}],"，有些雇主可能会晚点寄送 1042-S。"]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"my-8 rounded-2xl bg-brand-pink/5 border border-brand-pink/20 p-6","children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"text-sm font-semibold text-brand-pinkdeep mb-4","children":"[30 秒自测你的 2026 报税身份]"}],["$","$Ld",null,{}]]}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold mt-12 mb-6 text-brand-ink","children":"第四步：IRS 替代方案 (Form 4852)"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"rounded-[20px] bg-brand-pink/10 p-6 my-6 pointer-events-none border border-brand-pink/20","children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"font-semibold text-brand-pinkdeep mb-2","children":"解决方案"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-sm text-brand-ink/80","children":["如果到 4 月份还没拿到 W-2，IRS 允许你使用 ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"Form 4852 (Substitute for Form W-2)"}],"。"]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-3 text-sm text-brand-ink/80","children":"如果你因为没收到 W-2 而错过 4 月 15 日截止日期，可能会面临 Late Filing Penalty（滞纳金）。使用 Form 4852 是 IRS 官方认可的补救措施，它能证明你已经尽力履行了纳税义务，对未来的绿卡或 H1B 申请更加保险。"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-6","children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"font-semibold text-brand-pinkdeep mb-2 text-center","children":"懒人专属：2026 版 W-2 数据自动换算工具"}],"$Le","$Lf"]}],"$L10","$L11","$L12"]}],"$L13"]}]}]}]}],[